title: Veeam Backup Proxies
agents: veeam_rest
catalog: app/veeam
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors Veeam backup proxy status via the REST API.

 It reports:
 - Proxy type (VMware, Hyper-V, General Purpose)
 - Online/offline status
 - Enabled/disabled status
 - Outdated component warnings

 The check returns:
 - OK: Proxy is online and enabled
 - WARN: Proxy is disabled or has outdated components
 - CRIT: Proxy is offline
 - UNKNOWN: No data or proxy not found

item:
 The proxy name

discovery:
 One service is created for each backup proxy.
